entry.title: AndrewHazelden/Mikromedia-Gaming-Shield-Input-Library
entry.summary: This is an input library for the MikroElektronika Mikromedia Gaming Shield. It is compatible with the Mikromedia dsPIC33 and PIC32 boards. The library is designed to get you started with the Gaming Shield and provides control over the 4 LEDs on the Gaming Shield and reads the inputs from the buttons.
